Basic setup instructions
------------------------

* Copy protected/config/local-sample.php to protected/config/local.php and edit to suit
* Create MySQL database and import initial db from protected/migrations/initial.sql.gz

Tortoise GIT
------------

To commit changes to local repository

* Right click -> Git commit => "master"
* Write message (comment)
* Click OK
* (Optional) push committed changes to github by clicking Push

To push changes to github

* Right click -> Tortoise GIT -> Push
* OK

To updates local repository

* Right click -> Tortoise GIT -> Pull
* OK

You can also use sync to do a lot of this

* Right click -> Git Sync...
* Pull or push as required